The only thing you should know about wine is when you're looking at bottles 
in the store, check for a little pink paper band around the neck of the 
bottle. That label indicates that it's been harvested from a very good 
vineyard and that it's a high quality wine. If it's labeled you can trust 
even wine that costs like 2 bucks.﻿
